lead_paragraph: Keeper Simon Mignolet proved the shootout hero as Liverpool reached the League Cup final on penalties after a gripping last-four second leg tie at Anfield ended 1-1 on aggregate on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Liverpool Reach League Cup Final After Penalty Drama
